, about three months after the transaction closed.=C2=A0</p>
</blockquote>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">I <a href=3D"https://link.mail.bloombergbusine=
ss.com/click/30414414.272006/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYmxvb21iZXJnLmNvbS9vcGluaW9uL2=
FydGljbGVzLzIwMjMtMDEtMjYvY2hhdGdwdC1pcy1ub3QtbXVjaC1vZi1hLXBpdGNoLXJvYm90P=
