 not below the number of shares thereof then outstanding) by the affirmativ=
e vote of the holders of a majority of the stock of the corporation entitle=
d to vote irrespective of this subsection, if so provided in the original c=
ertificate of incorporation.=E2=80=9D And <a href=3D"https://link.mail.bloo=
mbergbusiness.com/click/30414414.272006/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuc2VjLmdvdi9BcmNoaXZ=
